    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The engine starts up without issue and the transmission remains fully functional, though you may notice some minor lag during acceleration. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic buttons that are finicky. It is a solid, honest car that has been regularly serviced but will require some upcoming routine maintenance to keep it in peak operating form.",
