    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine cabin, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to ensure a driving experience indistinguishable from new. Professional inspections are welcomed to verify its impeccable state.",
      "price": 46850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
